    "RQ1": "Can AMOS detect analytical-state violations without rejecting valid analytical SQL?",
    "RQ2": "Does AMOS improve safe and correct completion for live analytical agents under matched model and tool access?",
    "RQ3": "Does claim-level provenance improve reviewer error detection or reduce audit time?",
    "RQ4": "What latency, throughput, storage, consistency, and failure-recovery cost is imposed by AMOS at production-like scale?"
